{"tid":1283571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無做錯點解要蒙面？","createTime":"2019-07-04T00:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T00:54:04.000Z","uid":52942,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9982dad38e81fa4d02ca213ef125f781f51e499","tid":1283571,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:19:10.000Z","msg":"John Blake: When you started, why the mask? .<br />\nBruce Wayne/Batman: To protect the people closest to me.<br />\nJohn Blake: Yeah, but you're a loner, right? You didn't have any family.<br />\nBruce Wayne/Batman: There are always people you care about. You just don't realize how much until they're gone. The idea was to be a symbol. Batman could be anybody, that was the point<br />\n<br />\nTDK世界第一"},{"pid":"e81cf9e23e62d8457921f50b91360ca8666c943e","tid":1283571,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:25:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-kql4tda9TQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-kql4tda9TQ&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=54ca5855\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-kql4tda9TQ</a>"},{"pid":"17706cc0c22a19d577dbf1b3c05d415d12f89873","tid":1283571,"uid":206617,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:34:08.000Z","msg":"其實冇做錯呢樣本來真係唔洗蒙面<br />\n但家下呢個世界是非不分、黑白不分<br />\n有義士30號俾人打都俾人告番轉頭<br />\n班友一邊鳩嗌支持警察嚴正執法，一邊係警察面前打人，警察可以無視既<br />\n家下情況就係，立法、執法，甚至係審既都有可能係佢地既野<br />\n呢個是非顛倒既世界，講細聲啲會被人無視、老屈，講大聲啲真係唔洗保講自己？<br />\n<br />\n最後，我無野講了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4099903a0ed25e3033bbc6be7303bf147a009b1","tid":1283571,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:34:55.000Z","msg":"我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"ec3bb0c6e0a4c69f807d7faddd9474bd609565b3","tid":1283571,"uid":273791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:35:23.000Z","msg":"四隻字，白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e425c2b57b991b1d3299652d904b8e5efe4d7b","tid":1283571,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"我冇野講 <br />\n我要搵律師 (冇電話就問佢拎律師聯絡冊)<br />\n冇律師 我唔簽任何文件<br />\n我有權唔解鎖<br />\n我要食飯 飲水 拎毛氈 去廁所<br />\n我唔舒服想去醫院"}]}